    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver-focused example benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul, ensuring the individual throttle bodies deliver immediate throttle response across the powerband. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the internals are robust, recently undergoing a shim-and-bucket valve adjustment to maintain peak volumetric efficiency. This is a purist-spec machine optimized for mechanical longevity and tactile performance.",
